qDef.qDef:
IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based',

  IF(dimNum=1,num(count({1<LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"},[Access Type] = {'Login','User'}> } DISTINCT UserId),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=2,num(Ceil(Count({1<[Access Type]={'Login'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UsageId)/10)+ Count({1<[Access Type]={'User'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=3,num(Count({1<[Access Type]={'User'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'), 
  IF(dimNum=4,num(ceil(count({1<[Access Type]={'Login'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UsageId)/10),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=5,num(ceil((Ceil(Count({1<[Access Type]={'Login'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UsageId)/10)+ Count({1<[Access Type]={'User'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId))/7),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=6,num(max({1} Aggr(Nodistinct (Ceil(Count({1<[Access Type]={'Login'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UsageId)/10)
          + Count({1<[Access Type]={'User'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId)),Date)),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=7,num(Count({1<LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} DISTINCT usage_denied_access_id),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=8,num(Sum({1<LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} [License Allocation]),'#,##0'),' ' ))))))))

,
  IF(dimNum=1,num(count({1<LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"},[Access Type] = {"*"}> } DISTINCT UserId),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=2,num(Count({1<UserId={"=Min({1} [Access Date])>=ReloadTime()-6"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=3,num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Sense"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'), 
  IF(dimNum=4,num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Sense"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=4.5,num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Sense"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=5,num(Ceil(Count({1<[Access Type]={"*"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId)/7),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=6,num(max({1} Aggr(Nodistinct Count({1<[Access Type]={"*"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),Date)),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=7,num(Count({1<LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} DISTINCT usage_denied_access_id),'#,##0'),
  IF(dimNum=8,num(Sum({1<LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} [License Allocation]),'#,##0'),
  IF(qlikview_license_logs_present=1,
  	IF(dimNum=3.1,num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'), 
  	IF(dimNum=4.1,num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
  	IF(dimNum=4.8,num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-6))"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),' ')
    )))  
  )))))))))
)

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=IF(license_type_enabled='Token-based','Login Access token usage for Last 90 Days is based on the last 28 days.',
	IF(qlikview_license_logs_present=1,'In the past 28 days, QlikView accounted for: ' 
    	& num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-27))"}>} distinct UserId)
        		/Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Professional"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-27))"}>} distinct UserId),'0%')
                & ' of the Professional Users, '
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-27))"}>} distinct UserId)
        		/Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-27))"}>} distinct UserId),'0%')
                & ' of the Analyzer Users, and '
        & num(Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-27))"}>} distinct UserId)
        		/Count({1<[Unified Licensing Product]={"*"},[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-27))"}>} distinct UserId),'0%')
                & ' of the Analyzer Capacity Users.',' ')     
)

qValueExpression.qExpr:
=IF([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]>5, 
	(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1))+1)*[License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/28,		// Alert the viewer if their current month's usage rate will lead to running out
 6)	// If no Analyzer Capacity Time allocated, then this limit should never be exceeded

=IF([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]>5,  	(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1))+1)*[License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/45,  6)	// If no Analyzer Capacity Time allocated, then this limit should never be exceeded
